These new zones are not PoP zones, they are for those who are trying to get to 55 and 60, and having trouble in pop zones.  They are a little like pop zones though, in they are best for groups, not soloers, at least not for exp.  I will say a good thing about loot in these zones compared to BoT.  At least mobs here drop some cash items to sell to vendors, while in BoT, you can clear one whole wing and never see a thing, not even from the mini boss and one time, only the 4 slot combine ring from the main boss in that wing.  We even cleared one staircase past the cy, and found nada.  <br>
<br>
Alot of PoP zones are becoming exp zones only and getting quiet boring.  I'm glad they went back to mobs dropping trinkets to vendor sell.  Go to PoNb and clear to Therris and you might get a few bonechips to give to a necro.<br>
